    <p>BPC-157 at 250 mcg twice daily. Consider adding KPV peptide at 200 mcg daily for extra anti-inflammatory support. Apply topical GHK-Cu to affected <a href="/articles/best-peptides-for-joint-health">joints</a>.</p>
